<h1 operator="" class="">Motion</h1><h2>Selectable positions</h2><p>Neomacs try to keep the focus at selectable positions after every command invocation.</p><ul><li operator=""><span class="comma-expr" operator=""><div class="list" operator=""><span class="symbol" operator="">fundoc</span><span class="symbol">'selectable-p</span></div></span></li><li><span class="comma-expr" operator=""><div class="list" operator=""><span class="symbol" operator="">fundoc</span><span class="symbol">'selectable-p-aux</span></div></span></li></ul><h2>Motion by nodes and elements</h2><ul><li operator=""><span class="comma-expr" operator=""><div class="list" operator=""><span class="symbol" operator="">fundoc</span><span class="symbol">'forward-node</span></div></span></li><li><span class="comma-expr" operator=""><div class="list" operator=""><span class="symbol" operator="">fundoc</span><span class="symbol">'backward-node</span></div></span></li><li><span class="comma-expr" operator=""><div class="list" operator=""><span class="symbol" operator="">fundoc</span><span class="symbol">'forward-node-cycle</span></div></span></li><li><span class="comma-expr" operator=""><div class="list" operator=""><span class="symbol" operator="">fundoc</span><span class="symbol">'backward-node-cycle</span></div></span></li><li><span class="comma-expr" operator=""><div class="list" operator=""><span class="symbol" operator="">fundoc</span><span class="symbol">'forward-element</span></div></span></li><li><span class="comma-expr" operator=""><div class="list" operator=""><span class="symbol" operator="">fundoc</span><span class="symbol">'backward-element</span></div></span></li><li><span class="comma-expr" operator=""><div class="list" operator=""><span class="symbol" operator="">fundoc</span><span class="symbol">'backward-up-node</span></div></span></li></ul><h2>Top-level motion</h2><ul><li operator=""><span class="comma-expr" operator=""><div class="list" operator=""><span class="symbol" operator="">fundoc</span><span class="symbol">'beginning-of-defun</span></div></span></li><li><span class="comma-expr" operator=""><div class="list" operator=""><span class="symbol" operator="">fundoc</span><span class="symbol">'end-of-defun</span></div></span></li><li><span class="comma-expr" operator=""><div class="list" operator=""><span class="symbol" operator="">fundoc</span><span class="symbol">'beginning-of-buffer</span></div></span></li><li><span class="comma-expr" operator=""><div class="list" operator=""><span class="symbol" operator="">fundoc</span><span class="symbol">'end-of-buffer</span></div></span></li></ul><h2>Word motion</h2><ul><li operator=""><span class="comma-expr" operator=""><div class="list" operator=""><span class="symbol" operator="">fundoc</span><span class="symbol">'word-boundary-list</span></div></span></li><li><span class="comma-expr" operator=""><div class="list" operator=""><span class="symbol" operator="">fundoc</span><span class="symbol">'word-character-p</span></div></span></li><li><span class="comma-expr" operator=""><div class="list" operator=""><span class="symbol" operator="">fundoc</span><span class="symbol">'word-start-p</span></div></span></li><li><span class="comma-expr" operator=""><div class="list" operator=""><span class="symbol" operator="">fundoc</span><span class="symbol">'word-end-p</span></div></span></li></ul><p>Word motion commands:</p><ul><li><span class="comma-expr" operator=""><div class="list" operator=""><span class="symbol" operator="">fundoc</span><span class="symbol">'forward-word</span></div></span></li><li><span class="comma-expr" operator=""><div class="list" operator=""><span class="symbol" operator="">fundoc</span><span class="symbol">'backward-word</span></div></span></li></ul><h2>Line motion</h2><p>Test if position is at line boundary:</p><p><ul operator=""><li operator=""><span class="comma-expr" operator=""><div class="list" operator=""><span class="symbol" operator="">fundoc</span><span class="symbol">'block-elem